# *(_:_:)

**Operator**

Multiplies two quaternions and produces their product.

## Declaration

```swift
static func * (lhs: simd_quatd, rhs: simd_quatd) -> simd_quatd
```

## Discussion

The function returns the left-hand side quaternion rotated by the right-hand side quaternion.
